title: SAS T01 - A Pact With The Devil (Quentin-Choky-Onairam) cbr
description:
In a Belgrade riddled with corruption and ravaged by years of war, Milorad Lukovic, the former commander, of the red berets, one of the most terrible forces during the war, guilty of numerous atrocities and wanted by the International Criminal Court, is a hunted man... But remains elusive, thanks to many who prefer the old system. However Lukovic has ordered the assassination of Serbian Prime Minister and the Americans want his head. They send their best agent Prince Malko Linge ...

enjoy
